pple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\u003B\"> </span>The customer is responsible for all return shipping costs.</li>\r\n<li class=\"li1\" style=\"margin:0px\u003Bfont-size:11px\u003Bline-height:normal\u003Bfont-family:\'Helvetica Neue\'\u003B\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"line-height:normal\u003Bfont-family:Helvetica\u003Bcolor:#c7c8c9\u003B\"></span><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\u003B\"> </span>We recommend that you use a trackable shipping method and purchase shipping insurance, as we are not responsible for lost or damaged packages.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin:0px\u003Bline-height:normal\u003Bfont-family:\'Helvetica Neue\'\u003B\">Once we have received your return and confirmed that the conditions above have been met, we will issue a refund to your original payment method within [number of days] days.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin:0px\u003Bline-height:normal\u003Bfont-family:\'Helvetica Neue\'\u003B\">If you received a damaged or defective item, please contact us within [number of days] days of delivery and we will arrange for a replacement or refund.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin:0px\u003Bline-height:normal\u003Bfont-family:\'Helvetica Neue\'\u003B\">Thank you for shopping with us, and please don’t hesitate to contact us if you have any questions or concerns.</p> ' 
