(6, 2, 1, 'Personal data protection policy', '', '', '', '<p style=\"margin:0px\u003Bcolor:#353535\u003Bfont-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif\u003Bfont-size:16px\u003Btext-align:justify\u003Bbackground-color:#ffffff\u003B\">It is normal to place special emphasis on how your data is obtained, used and shared.</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0px\u003Bcolor:#353535\u003Bfont-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif\u003Bfont-size:16px\u003Btext-align:justify\u003Bbackground-color:#ffffff\u003B\"> </p>\n<p style=\"margin:0px\u003Bcolor:#353535\u003Bfont-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif\u003Bfont-size:16px\u003Btext-align:justify\u003Bbackground-color:#ffffff\u003B\">That is why this personal data protection policy (the “<span style=\"font-weight:bold\u003B\">Policy</span>”) has been created to help you understand the practices and conditions in which PrestaShop SA - a public limited company entered the Paris company and trade register under no. 497 916 635, having its offices at 4, rue Jules Lefebvre, 75009, Paris, (“<span style=\"font-weight:bold\u003B\">PrestaShop</span>”) gathers, uses and stores your personal data (the “<span style=\"font-weight:bold\u003B\">Data</span>”).</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0px\u003Bcolor:#353535\u003Bfont-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif\u003Bfont-size:16px\u003Btext-align:justify\u003Bbackground-color:#ffffff\u003B\"> </p>\n<p style=\"margin:0px\u003Bcolor:#353535\u003Bfont-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif\u003Bfont-size:16px\u003Btext-align:justify\u003Bbackground-color:#ffffff\u003B\">In this document you will find the various Data that we may collect and process or that you may provide to us when you access :</p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top:0px\u003Bmargin-bottom:11px\u003Bcolor:#353535\u003Bfont-family:\'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Verdana, sans-serif\u003Bfont-size:16px\u003Btext-align:justify\u003Bbackground-color:#ffffff\u003B\">\n<li>The <a href=\"https://prest